archimate:ApplicationComponent.name: Remote Relay Management System - eProtect
archimate:ApplicationComponent.documentation:
ETAP eProtect consists of a real-time server and a client interface for the purpose of establishing a centralized asset management system for transmission & distribution equipment. ETAP eProtect consists of a user-friendly & multi-user application that utilizes Web based thin clients for data manipulation in conjunction with desktop clients for advanced applications.
